Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.26,0:00:25.22,Bible,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000)\pos(712.253,286)}{\pos(362.253,130)}And I saw a beast rising out of the sea, with ten horns and seven heads;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:25.22,Bible,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000)}{\pos(712.253,370)}and on its horns were ten diadems, and on its heads were blasphemous names.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:25.22,Bible,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000)}{\pos(712.253,456)}The dragon gave the beast his power and his throne and great authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.32,0:00:25.22,Bible,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000)}{\pos(712.253,546)}They worshiped the dragon, for he had given authority to the beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:25.22,Bible,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000)}{\pos(712.253,626)}and they worshiped the beast, saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:25.22,Bible,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000)}{\pos(712.253,716)}"Who is like the beast,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:25.22,Bible,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000)}{\pos(712.253,800)}and who can fight against it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:25.22,Bible,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000)}{\pos(712.253,855)}Revelations 13:1-4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-That was amazing.\N-You were great as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.14,0:00:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That was such a difficult brain aneurysm,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,but you did the clipping so speedily.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.56,0:00:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an excellent surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Herr Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I could once again witness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the genius of Kenzo Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I couldn't have done it\Nwithout everyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.28,0:01:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it's so late in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.58,0:01:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was a six-hour surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have any outpatients today.\NGet some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:30.90,Titles1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\pos(735.774,555.75)}1986
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:30.90,Titles1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\pos(738.028,679.5)}Düsseldorf
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:30.90,Titles1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\pos(740.282,798.75)}{\pos(735.774,798.75)}Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:59.30,Names,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000)\pos(720.022,1035)}KENZO TENMA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,95)}Our roles are reversed, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.67,Names,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000)\pos(720.022,1035)}EVA HEINEMANN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,150)}I should be the one being woken\Nwith kisses like a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva. It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now in Düsseldorf. Mr. Lyman?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo, did you forget about our date?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Liebert, an adviser in the East German\NTrade Bureau, has arrived to seek asylum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He appeared in front of the reporters\Nwith his family yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. and Mrs. Liebert appeared to be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Their son and daughter,\Na pair of fraternal twins,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,looked happy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They will be staying in Düsseldorf\Nfor a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The government will be taking care\Nof their well-being.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't slept a wink...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.39,0:04:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wake up! It's your news!\N-…the opera singer Mr. Rosenbach
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,was in a critical condition\Ndue to a hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He is now in a stable condition\Nfollowing surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.06,0:04:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The operation was\Nat Eisler Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Earlier, the hospital's director\NDr. Heinemann held a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,195)}Mr. Rosenbach was diagnosed\Nwith a ruptured brain aneurysm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:09.50,Heinemann,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000)\pos(698.941,1019)}Dr. Heinemann
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,160)}The surgery went smoothly,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and the clipping was very successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.37,0:05:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell us his chance of recovery\Nas he has many fans waiting for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We will give it our best to help him\Nget his voice back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Heinemann's team has performed\Nnumerous complex surgeries in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This surgery has certainly confirmed\Nour country's status
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in the medical community.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this great, Kenzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about me.\NIt's news about your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.19,0:05:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's all because you did\Nthe perfect surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,as one of father's team members.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he appreciates that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one getting the hospital\Nsuch great recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because of your father
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that I can work in Germany like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Kenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything will be okay if you just\Nfollow father's lead and do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time before\Nhe becomes board chairman at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.72,0:06:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And you will soon be Chief of Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, you'll be the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be the Director's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not built for a hard life,\Nso you'd better make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go out, or…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure is 128/64.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain spatula.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now to trim the medullary pyramid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, your surgery\Nwas excellent as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.31,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:03.40,Names,,0,0,0,,{\fad(850,1000){\pos(720.,1035)}DR. BECKER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,150)}And surgery isn't\Nthe only thing you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Being Head of Neurosurgery at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Director and Chief of Surgery\Nboth favor you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.95,0:07:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You even have the heart\Nof the Director's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say, Dr. Becker?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I don't mean anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just that it's all politics\Nin the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you know that the Director\Nis just using you. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He talked about the opera singer's surgery\Nas if he was the one who operated
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,during the televised press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, being used is proof\Nthat you have the skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're promoted,\Ndon't forget about me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy you a drink some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring my husband back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I want him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.27,0:08:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you do his surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband was brought into the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,before that opera singer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.45,0:08:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But you put off his operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the best doctor\Nin this hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why!? Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was about to perform the surgery\Non the Turkish construction worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Operation Room One immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Director's order. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You... If you had operated on him,\Nhe would have been saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.74,0:09:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You...\N-Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him back to me. Give him back!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,…and I was fighting over\Nthat dress with my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the only dress of that size.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry, I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey, are you listening?\N-Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I read the records.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Becker did the surgery\Non that Turkish man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.69,0:09:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He obviously took too long\Nto perform the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If I did the surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that Turkish man could have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that. We're having dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, what did she want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.13,0:10:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I only followed the Director's order
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to do the opera singer's surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,\Npeople's lives aren't created equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Give him back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...to me! ...to me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the neighbor called the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.68,0:11:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How many gunshots?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,About five to six.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who lives in that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's… where the East German defector\NMr. Liebert has been staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What? This could be problematic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,On my count of three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a survivor! It's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A man and a woman are dead,\Nand a boy is in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeat, a boy is in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,An emergency…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bullet in the head?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the boy the only patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Both of his parents are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it was a robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll be at the hospital\Nin five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Heinemann, I'm sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to have kept your daughter out\Nso late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.23,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Eva's fiancé,\Nso don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you come in for a cup of tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you told your parents in Japan\Nabout the wedding date?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But my father is a doctor\Nat a small private practice,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't know if he would have\Ntime to come to Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a good chance
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for him to come\Nand enjoy a bit of traveling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.43,0:13:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! It'd be our pleasure to have him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very grateful to you\Nfor taking me under your wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,When you came to Germany,\NI thought you were like a high school boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're the up-and-coming\Ntop surgeon at Eisler Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kenzo, about your research
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,on cerebral vasospasm following\Nsubarachnoid hemorrhage…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm making a model of a dog\Nwith subarachnoid hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we're canceling\Nthe research project.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be a presenter\Nat the next symposium
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,of the European Society\Nfor Emergency Medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like you to prepare my speech draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost done with my research--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a tough afternoon today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Some shady group came to the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and protested about the surgery\Nfor the opera singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They said that we put off\Nthe Turkish man's surgery for the singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a total misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.68,0:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Turkish man's surgery\Nwas performed earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing wrong with our procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh… Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.26,0:15:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they think doctors\Nare volunteers or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to advance as academic scholars\Nbefore we can save lives. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you for my manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I have high hopes for you, Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes… Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-How is the patient?\N-He's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How are his vitals?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure is 72/50.\NPulse rate is 137.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.62,0:16:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet entered from his forehead…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.42,0:16:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me the X-rays.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.25,0:16:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What about this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She is the boy's twin sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:16:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Any injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, but she has suffered\Nsevere mental trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The X-rays and CT scans\Nof his head are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It entered deep into the brain\Nfrom his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.09,0:17:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The bullet grazed\Nhis left middle cerebral artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.35,0:17:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Dr. Tenma is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we moved the bullet even a little,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the artery might break\Nand lead to hemorrhaging.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Becker.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.87,0:17:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be late\Nwhen you're the one on duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll do a bifrontal craniotomy,\Nclean up any bones and infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll carefully\Ntake the bullet out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, we'll do angioplasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It will take some time,\Nbut let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood pressure is 120/80\Nand pulse rate is 92. Looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.64,0:18:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Anesthetic applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.24,0:18:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,-Dr. Tenma.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to Operating Room One right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayor Roedecker has collapsed\Nwith cerebral thrombus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He will arrive in ten minutes\Nby helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please call Dr. Boyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He might have an arterial occlusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case,\Nyou will do the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm about to start\Non the surgery for that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.20,0:19:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Tenma, I'm leaving you to take care of the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got Dr. Eisen and Dr. Boyer coming
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.46,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,so it should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm just getting ready\Nfor another surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You can let Dr. Becker handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.22,0:19:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest with you,\Nmy current patient's
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,left middle cerebral artery\Nwas grazed by a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be a very complicated surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Boyer can operate on the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to be the one\Nto operate on the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.69,0:19:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, you must do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to save the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor has promised that\Nhe will increase
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,our hospital's subsidy\Nduring the next medical audit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let him die just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:20:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Tenma.\NI have high hopes for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor has arrived at the heliport!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.60,0:20:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do an angiogram after the CT scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Check where the thrombotic occlusion is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're relying on your genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they think doctors\Nare volunteers or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to advance as academic scholars\Nbefore we can save lives. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I only followed the Director's order
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,to do the opera singer's surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.94,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.52,0:20:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,After all,\Npeople's lives aren't created equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you did his surgery,\Nhe might have lived!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.59,0:21:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.14,0:21:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another surgery to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.35,0:21:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.36,0:21:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Director's order!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The mayor is having a CT scan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go to the CT scan room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.65,0:21:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.87,0:21:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Hang in there. I will save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:36.95,ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1076)\i1\fad(800,880)\1}And slowly, you come to realise
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.30,0:22:45.80,ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1076)\i1\fad(800,880)\1}It's all as it should be{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:54.30,ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1076)\i1\fad(800,880)\1}You can only do so much{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.00,0:22:59.48,ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1076)\i1\fad(800,880)\1}If you're game enough{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.48,0:23:07.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1076)\i1\fad(800,880)\1}You could place your trust in me\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.08,0:23:16.34,ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1076)\i1\fad(800,880)\1}For the love of life\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:21.64,ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1100)\i1\fad(800,880)\1}There's a trade off\N\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.30,0:23:27.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1100)\i1\fad(800,880)\1}We could lose it all\N\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.80,0:23:33.84,ED,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,1100)\i1\fad(800,880)\1}But we'll go down fighting\N\N{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.57,0:03:25.57,Titles1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\pos(728,754)}Herr Dr. Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.04,0:23:53.55,Titles1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(728,754)}Downfall
